{
  "description": "A close-up, interior view of a vibrant red tulip flower. The petals are deeply saturated in a rich crimson, curving and folding inwards to create a dramatic, enveloping effect. The flower's center showcases bright yellow stamens topped with dark brown, pollen-covered anthers. The petals have a slight texture and translucency near the edges, allowing some light to pass through. The overall composition emphasizes the intricate details of the flower\u2019s reproductive parts.",
